        <updateDate>2006-01-07T18:39:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Household Energy and Taxpayer Assistance Act of 2005 - Provides additional appropriations for the low-income home energy assistance program for FY2006.</p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow individual taxpayers a refundable tax credit for 20% of their residential energy expenses. Imposes a $200 lifetime limitation on such credit ($300 for joint returns).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
